data.description: This home is one-of-a-kind in a peaceful, private setting on almost ½ acre! WELCOME HOME to this charming brick ranch conveniently located near schools and shopping. So many newer items including furnace and AC, siding, gutters, bedroom carpeting, LVT flooring, front windows, and more.  As you enter notice the large home office with floor-to-ceiling windows offering great natural light.  In addition, this home boasts a large family room with fireplace big enough for all your family and friend gatherings.  Adjacent is the eat-in kitchen with painted cabinets and a spacious pantry.  The fenced backyard includes a sizeable freeform patio, raised garden beds, and a storage shed.  This north-facing patio is perfect for morning coffee or evening BBQs.  Primary bedroom with en-suite bath has a quiet peaceful vibe perfect after a long day.  In addition to the hall linen closet don't miss the built-in storage/display area. The basement is large and perfect for storage or future finish.  This picturesque home on almost ½ acre is a rare find and won't last.  Come take a look and make this your new home!
